snippet.title: Set Sail! Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
This be but a taste of the adventures you and your crew will have on the seas of Set Sail! 

Fight, Sail and Cooperate in our 4 Player Couch Co-op Pirate Party Game. 

Look out for a Demo, docking on itch.io later this month. 🏴‍☠️

Linktree - linktr.ee/dragonscalestudios

Scored by our incredible composer Ben Randall, bringing sizzling shanties and pirate tunes to the seas of Set Sail!
 https://twitter.com/BenRComposer
